Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伯特小队 科尔小队
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应对敌舰哨机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余部队暂时保持距离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织突击阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人防守严密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来很难摧毁抵御光子环阵列的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫队全员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起 我指挥你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即汇合一处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会战斗 不论敌人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这机动…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他明明不是X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要 打败你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打败你 保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法完全成为战士的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今非昔比了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂兵全给我死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要失去冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没队长那么成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敏克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电磁终端 开始在轨道部署
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会不会一再光顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至多只能发射一到两次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部署还要多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使改变角度发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这样还是会被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能指望明日野司令了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射线轴上发现敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的极有可能是攻击电磁终端
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽调机动战士来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何也要守住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.16,0:05:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据推测那是要塞姿态控制系统的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座要塞为抵御攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行了整体调头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即是说 掩体只能防御来自固定方向的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为求直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有先打坏姿态控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间不多 我马上开始使用祖法尔特火箭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围敌人就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引住敌人就是了对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝 维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要塞行动受限
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可以对其造成伤害 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 实施光子爆破炮的指向发射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要塞 紧急转向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有被防御的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 使用机动战士的推进器转动要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达 确实敌你不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即使是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让精神力头盔满负荷运转…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙不要命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算得了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特 大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为维甘指引未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达孜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何我也要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非实现不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令 您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我回歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们重新组织后 返回战线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子环阵列的防线岌岌可危
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支撑不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 请暂时中断发射程序
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把光子爆破炮的目标设定权交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃尔中士 让出操作席
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知全体机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤离射线轴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子爆破炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干涉掩体机能停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲击造成推进系统重创
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人机动战士开始撤退后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有机动战士暂时撤离敌人要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待进一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 总算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要塞的推进系统完全停转
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此下去会和诺德拉姆相撞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即通知诺德拉姆政府紧急避难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要塞失去了盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定用光子环阵列毁了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 连射可能造成舰船无法航行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不发射的话诺德拉姆就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有放手一搏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就现在 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子爆破炮 指向发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键时刻能量不足…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号动力室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入炮击后功率调整模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要塞移速放缓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在偏离与诺德拉姆的撞击轨道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向本舰飞来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往左紧急避让
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 准备应对撞击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会和敌人要塞一同坠入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉落地面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难免造成巨大伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先逃离要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 集结舰队全力应对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用光子爆破炮打开突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 发射系统部件损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要更换发射口侧面的共振控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上去换
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更换零件？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…明白了 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 情况明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离进入大气层 还有180分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更换完成 这样随时可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴们的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让你们一死了之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事 滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米 你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光子爆破炮 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米 等着我 马上来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…看来回不去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想和奥布莱特成为一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…孤单一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号是我们的家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说好要回家的 一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是我们的家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米… 蕾米…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾米！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坠落…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去地球会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆来电
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进入内部 引爆能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以赶在坠入大气层前破坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但已经没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 难道想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我 可以救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只有我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…一度不知为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被焦躁和仇恨冲昏头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 现在我已不再迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心只想保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请允许我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 如此下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座达乌内斯会对地球造成严重危害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 只能执行备案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 要塞自爆装置失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我想办法搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 直接去能量核心？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照备案 将登陆胶囊投放地球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须在要塞爆炸同时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混在残骸中 投放胶囊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看准时机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球是伊甸之地 必须救它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有控制的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Rounder之力 让我尽情使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算从内部摧毁这座要塞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你休想阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但内部构造复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入深处的话 会来不及返回
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算用高达撞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要引爆能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用卫星摧毁器 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我指示引爆位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不可能失败的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道伊泽尔坎特大人一早就打算这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到又能并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为维甘的战士 我战斗至今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为实现维甘的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人的力量 实在太过渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不至于
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是救了许多人的性命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这只是想保住我们伊甸的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球是…伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决心建造伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不为战争和疾病受苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乐土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你战斗的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经连自己为何而战也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋里装满了对你和父亲的嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你身在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,置身险境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也成了战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有事需要你去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能去外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问了 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要塞碎片因爆炸进入低空轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对地球的影响降低到最小限度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时确认高达逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入射角固定 进入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号随行进入大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去救亚瑟姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能扔下AGE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想开创的 维甘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 为争夺这美丽的自然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.99,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在进行战争
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此赤红的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.53,0:22:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到
